headline: McKesson Corporation Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: IRVING, Texas, October 30, 2025--The Board of Directors of McKesson Corporation (NYSE:MCK) yesterday declared a regular dividend of 82 cents per share of common stock. The dividend will be payable on January 2, 2026 to shareholders of record on December 1, 2025.

headline: Cardinal Health (CAH) Surpasses Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Cardinal (CAH) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +15.38% and +8.39%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
